### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 系统资源使用率
POST https://10.182.63.222/hardware/getNetInit
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 系统资源使用率
POST https://10.182.63.222/hardware/per
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 服务监控
POST https://10.182.63.222/hardware/getServerStatues
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 系统告警列表
POST https://10.182.63.222/hardware/getSyswarnList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}} &
pageSize = 15 &
page = 1 &
orderField = time &
order = desc

