token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 LICENSE授权
POST https://10.182.63.222/license/index
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 授权信息下载
GET https://10.182.63.222/license/getCpuSerialize?sn=DOG2024
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 授权激活
POST https://10.182.63.222/license/active
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="csrf_token"

{{token}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="DOG2024.cer"
Content-Type: application/x-x509-ca-cert

< DOG2024.cpu
--WebAppBoundary

