### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 升级列表
POST https://10.182.63.222/upgrade/getUpgradeList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}} &
page = 1 &
pageSize = 15 &
order = desc &
orderField = createTime

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 手动上传升级文件
POST https://10.182.63.222/upgrade/uploadFile
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="csrf_token"

{{token}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="upfile"; filename="DOG2024.tar.gz"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< DOG2024.cpu
--WebAppBoundary

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 升级文件校验
POST https://10.182.63.222/upgrade/checkFile
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token = {{token}}

### SysAdmin/hillstone@2018 升级
